Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:38.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97550,98640}Well, I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:48.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107300,108610}I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:53.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111830,113970}Sandy is very happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:56.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114120,116070}She is riding the bike on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:00.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117740,120310}You both have to hurry a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:02.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120500,122850}I'll arrive to the palace before you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:06.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123310,126500}Well, I understand that you\Nwant to go there quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:08.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127470,128270}Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:10.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128420,130560}Do you still think about\Nwhat happened yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:11.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130880,131620}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:16.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132160,136420}It's not your fault, Colin,\Nbecause Priscilla left my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137250,138100}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:23.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138560,143990}No, if I wouldn't come to you quickly,\NPriscilla could have the cake with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:26.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144360,146580}You had no other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:29.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146720,149860}And also we do this now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:33.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149990,153700}Priscilla can eat the cake she made herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:34.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153910,154520}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154620,155360}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155480,157290}Enough, no "but"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:39.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157400,159340}John! Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:42.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160670,162120}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:43.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162230,163790}John, you still have the cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:46.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163820,166070}so I can't go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168300,169070}Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:49.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169190,169810}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170310,171270}Just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:55.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171350,175180}Don't move too much\Nso you don't spoil the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:56.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175370,176300}Ah oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:57.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176660,177360}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177380,178620}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178830,181070}It'll be fine! It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:05.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184720,185680}Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:06.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185860,186820}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188020,190170}I'm still on vacation from school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190270,192530}The schedule changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194510,196190}If you say so…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:20.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196640,200010}Tonight at 9 o'clock, the plane\Nwill come to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:23.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200360,203800}Stay in your room now and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204800,206720}That 's all, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:33.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212540,213710}Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:35.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214720,215750}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215860,217550}Why didn't you returned to your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217690,220810}Grandfather, you've always told me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:43.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220830,223840}that there are no sudden orders\Nfor no reason, have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225490,226300}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226560,228240}This is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:54.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229090,234590}If you think I'm listening to you directly and\Nwithout checking the cause, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:57.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234690,237930}But I will follow your orders\Nwhen you tell me the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:02.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238050,242120}I'm not your dog or your horse, grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:16.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252070,256530}You are the only one who always responds\Nto my orders, you are impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:20.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257630,260620}I'm honored to impress you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260780,263160}It's an honor to pay tribute\Nto your Guy Funeral of Mr. Denver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:27.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263730,267840}I don't think there is a better way than this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268000,269850}to express my gratitude to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:31.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270440,271330}Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:32.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272080,272570}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:37.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272670,277740}You are an important Duke.\NYou must attend the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278340,281430}That's why you should come back,\Ndid you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:42.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281670,282220}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282340,284400}You can return as long as you know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288440,290690}This means…\NGrandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290930,291870}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291970,293610}If you do not mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:57.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293700,297080}can I leave my room because\Nthere is no reason to stay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297340,298010}Hm…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:58.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298220,298820}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:00.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298850,300170}This is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:04.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300880,304850}So, during the day, I can go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:05.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304920,305730}Mhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307570,309750}That's it, my grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:14.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313650,314340}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:25.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322160,325000}I always wanted to take care of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325090,327830}but I can't do that as long as\NI have to go back to Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:31.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328470,331820}My grandfather is like my father now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:36.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331940,336020}I should therefore pay tribute\Nto the aristocrats there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:42.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338120,342070}I want to spend my childhood more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355530,358800}But I still have today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:15.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374670,375560}Heinz!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:19.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376190,379680}Do you want to get out of the palace again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379820,381130}I'll go to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:21.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381150,381700}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381900,382930}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383040,385280}Today I'll go walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:26.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385430,386810}I won't bother you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386920,388920}But this…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389000,390870}It's better not to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:31.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391010,391980}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:37.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392550,397030}I'm afraid you won't be able\Nto go to Scotland tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:40.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397250,400080}But there is still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:44.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401170,404810}But something else might happen\Nlike yesterday…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:48.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404810,408830}This way the plane will be delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:52.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409260,412350}I won't be late, I'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412410,413460}Ah… oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:59.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413620,419020}Of course, I don't doubt your words, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:02.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419510,422400}What if… an emergency happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422500,425700}In the end I'm the one responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:09.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425780,429890}I hope you think about those\Npeople who can fool you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:14.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433740,434730}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:17.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434820,437020}I won't bother you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:20.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438310,440000}Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443550,445590}This is much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452630,454230}Just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:36.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454310,456700}The door of the house is very far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456970,458870}No doubt it is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459000,461370}Because my dad comes here\Nto deliver the goods sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462310,463860}It doesn't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:46.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464410,466310}Maybe someone will come out if we shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466700,468590}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468700,470590}Is Priscilla here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:51.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470710,471890}Is it anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472060,473820}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475200,476400}What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:58.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476510,478310}Don't make noise in front of the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478600,480530}Sorry… Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480660,482650}We came to see Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:03.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483430,483940}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:07.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483970,487670}It's not tactful to call the princess\Nof this house by her name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:10.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488180,490190}You should call her Miss Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490450,491470}What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:14.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491810,494580}Should I call her Miss Priscilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497940,500390}Strange, this is really strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:22.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501090,502510}What is so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502630,504340}Priscilla is Priscilla, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:25.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504490,505680}What does this man mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505780,507100}Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:30.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507210,510400}Pff! You are just tiring!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510540,511470}And now, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511560,513330}Miss is very busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513850,515120}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:38.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515340,518150}We came to see Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518270,521530}Miss doesn't have time\Nto meet people like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521640,523430}Now, go back quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523630,525100}But we are…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525210,527640}We want to give this cake to Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:51.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528560,531090}Hey, you can't do what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:53.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532830,533720}Ah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534230,535710}If you stay here…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535770,538280}Although it's the cake that\NPriscilla made by herself…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538370,539660}W-w-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:05.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544090,545920}As if I would believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546060,547860}Get back quickly! Go go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:12.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551040,552710}As if I would believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:15.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552870,555390}She can't meet the children of the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:17.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555460,557180}Hm! You can never…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:24.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563640,564800}What is this guy talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:26.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564920,566270}It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:26.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566300,566960}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:33.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571240,573180}Lassie, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:35.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574740,575480}Ah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579590,580640}It's Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580750,582160}What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:43.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582730,583630}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:45.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583750,585210}All of you, have you come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:46.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585370,586330}Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587280,588940}I thought we wouldn't\Nbe able to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589040,590230}You exaggerate…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:56.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595450,596500}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:57.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596670,597870}Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:02.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598210,602930}That doorman whose eyes look like this!\NHe is the one who destroyed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603460,604790}Do you mean Heinz?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605620,606690}Looks like…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606690,608300}This is not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608400,609960}I'll make him pay for the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:10.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610060,610840}Pay the price?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:11.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610920,611990}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612610,613950}This…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:21.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620990,621690}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:27.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626340,627040}Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631030,633510}Miss! How did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637340,638070}Ah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638280,640640}How did you get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:50.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648990,650180}Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663120,664400}Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666950,668000}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670100,672420}What did you do, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:14.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673900,674910}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675000,676960}Did you think I was the Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677200,678020}Huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:20.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678180,680120}I just saw just before!
Comment: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:25.62,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:685623,685623}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:31.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688180,691390}John! Priscilla! Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:34.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693900,694990}How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:36.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695150,696510}Everything was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:39.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696680,699150}He came to me and when he fell into the trap
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:41.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699180,701200}he looked at me in the way\Nyou didn't look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702050,704150}His face was like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705180,707940}Even a ghost doesn't have a face like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:54.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711370,714060}I always wanted to wear such clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:11:59.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718330,719440}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719740,721840}I also like these clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:02.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721970,722630}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:03.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722780,723840}Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:07.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724310,727180}I love the smell of sunny straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:08.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727480,728270}Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:09.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728410,729120}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:16.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732830,736160}Why does everyone like the other dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:17.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736390,737350}It's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737880,739010}Listen, Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739130,741060}Let's plan what we'll today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741470,742470}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742650,744630}I want to see Moi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:28.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744770,748520}John said there was a rock\Nthat looked like a castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749430,750520}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:34.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750680,754610}But… Moi is too far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754800,756500}Can't we do that today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757240,758940}Not so, however…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758970,760550}I want to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:47.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763380,767630}If we go now to our castle\Nwe will reach it at sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767760,769170}I'm concerned about the return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769320,770800}Is there no shortcut?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:52.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771010,772580}Are you searching for a coal car track?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772670,774420}That bridge is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:55.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774550,775630}It's scary…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775700,776620}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776670,778080}I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:59.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778190,779500}You're a boy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779940,782070}But I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782710,784220}But Priscilla can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:04.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784300,784880}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785010,786830}Well, let's go to Moi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787020,788390}We decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788410,789720}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790330,792730}Priscilla, no problem to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821980,824530}The road will be fine\Nas long as it passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:54.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833710,834420}Eh…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835380,836420}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844120,845040}Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845200,846150}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846940,848710}Yes, I am fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848830,850720}I'm fine because I'm getting used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854000,855640}What is it, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856020,857600}Ah… Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858010,859150}Uh… uh-uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859800,861830}I can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:25.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864930,865810}Ahh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868090,870100}Ahh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872700,873700}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873830,875480}Don't look down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:38.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877950,878690}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879780,881220}Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:43.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881490,883060}First of all…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:46.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883130,886040}One two three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:54.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886890,894790}One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:56.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895350,896890}Are you okay, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:58.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897240,898290}He's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:04.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898540,904670}One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924170,925320}Look! Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:27.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925420,927310}What is it? I can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928260,930780}With the sun shining brightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949510,950960}Ah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957700,959900}This is our secret place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:02.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960630,962720}We are playing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962800,964720}Catching the names near here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966900,970110}From today, Priscilla will become\Nour friend in the Rocky Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:11.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970570,971590}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:12.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971730,972840}I'm very happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973370,975150}I understand how you feel in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975300,978560}John and the others, you are tempted every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:19.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978860,979880}Nager?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980040,982470}It's not like we're building\Nor something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983070,984350}You are lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984650,986490}I can't imagine all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986790,989630}Now you can imagine everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:30.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989840,990610}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:33.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993040,993850}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994150,996340}That's right, I can do that now…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:40.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996930,1000630}That means it's your first adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000790,1002450}Tomorrow is another adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002850,1004340}Will you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004640,1006810}The sun began to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:47.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007020,1007730}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:03.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019790,1023100}I can't go on an adventure tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:04.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024010,1024830}- Oh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:06.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025310,1026930}What's up, Priscilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027790,1030210}I want to climb up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:13.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030470,1033520}Up? Do you want to climb\Nto the top of the rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033670,1034590}Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:16.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035310,1036190}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:17.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036530,1037380}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:20.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037490,1040510}If we do that, the night will fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040640,1043420}But the sun is still bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043640,1046620}We can still climb to the top today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:31.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047410,1051670}Please John, Sandy, Colin! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052700,1053440}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060430,1062030}It's not possible? I thought…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:45.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062890,1065850}We should return before it's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066240,1067290}Priscilla…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:51.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068280,1071390}Could you come tomorrow…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071860,1073130}I want to climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073500,1076560}I still want climb to the top today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:03.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081120,1083970}Don't worry about such a ridiculous thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:05.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084540,1085440}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:07.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085470,1087560}Climb to the top as long as the sun is shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:08.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087820,1088760}Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089370,1090870}Do you usually climb through here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091050,1092060}I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:14.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092180,1094060}You follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:15.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094710,1095490}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095690,1097030}What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:20.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097160,1100460}The sun and sweating are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:22.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100880,1102260}Uh uh… Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103090,1104750}Priscilla, do you follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:28.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106790,1108400}There is still another way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119720,1121960}Priscilla, grab my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:06.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144310,1146720}Do your best, a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:24.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163340,1164330}Ah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:28.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167590,1168720}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191920,1195010}The horizon looks like a red ribbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198130,1199400}I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:01.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199500,1201580}And finally I was able to see it\Nfor the last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:02.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201610,1202910}The last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:03.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203100,1203920}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:07.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204050,1207140}I have to go back to Scotland tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207370,1208720}You said Scotland?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208900,1210220}Will you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210370,1212740}There is my real home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:17.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213050,1217330}There is no large place like this,\Nor flowers, or big rocks like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:20.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217530,1220300}But there are many things waiting for me…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:25.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221600,1225580}But I wanted to play together tomorrow\Nand go on an adventure like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228620,1229640}Priscilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:33.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231530,1233060}Come here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:38.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235680,1238970}Yes, certainly, and with all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251710,1254640}I thought we should return to\Nwhere Sandy's bike was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:55.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254750,1255620}Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:57.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255720,1257770}But they'll will punish us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257850,1258820}Eh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264350,1265490}You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:08.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265610,1268650}You don't know where your home is, and\Nyour parents, they're worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:09.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268680,1269320}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:10.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269550,1270580}Troublemaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:18.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274770,1278720}Oh, anyway, kids usually do things like that…
